        protected <T extends java.lang.annotation.Annotation> T findAnnotation(java.beans.PropertyDescriptor pd,
                                                           java.lang.Class<?> clazz,
                                                           java.lang.Class<T> annotationClazz)
        Find the annotation

        The following search order processed

        1. Check the field with the same name as the property, process through all superclasses
        2. Check the read method
        3. Check the write method

        Parameters:
        pd - the property descriptor to check
        clazz - class instance
        Returns:
        the annotation or null if none was found
